:<font size="15">רעה</font></div>

===Pronunciation===
רעה / râ‛âh / raw-aw'

===Etymology===
A primitive root; 

===Verb===
'''רעה'''

# to tend a flock, that is, pasture it; intransitively to graze (literally or figuratively); generally to rule; by extension to associate with (as a friend): -  X break, companion, keep company with, devour, eat up, evil entreat, feed, use as a friend, make friendship with, herdman, keep [sheep] (-er), pastor, + shearing house, shepherd, wander, waste.

